Package net.minestom.server.ping

Class ResponseData

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minestom.server.ping.ResponseData
  • public class ResponseData
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the data sent to the player when refreshing the server list.

    Filled by ResponseDataConsumer and specified in MinecraftServer.start(String, int, ResponseDataConsumer).
